semiprof
------------------------------------------
Simple thread safe annotation based C++ profiler

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.6.7-1
  libgcc1-13.4.0-1
  libsemiprof-devel-1.0+git20220709-1bl1
  libsemiprof1-1.0+git20220709-1bl1
  libstdc++6-13.4.0-1
  pkg-config-2.5.1-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.46-1
  cmake-4.2.1-1
  cygport-0.37.7-1
  gcc-core-13.4.0-1
  gcc-g++-13.4.0-1
  ninja-1.13.2-1

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/kabicm/semiprof

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/kabicm/semiprof.git

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack semiprof-1.0+git20220709-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./semiprof-1.0+git20220709-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/semiprof-1.0+git20220709-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/semiprof-1.0+git20220709-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libsemiprof1-1.0+git20220709-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libsemiprof-devel-1.0+git20220709-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(semiprof)
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/semiprof.README
  /usr/share/doc/semiprof/LICENSE
  /usr/share/doc/semiprof/todo.md

(libsemiprof1)
  /usr/bin/cygsemiprof-1.dll

(libsemiprof-devel)
  /usr/include/semiprof.hpp
  /usr/lib/cmake/semiprof/semiprofConfig-release.cmake
  /usr/lib/cmake/semiprof/semiprofConfig.cmake
  /usr/lib/cmake/semiprof/semiprofConfigVersion.cmake
  /usr/lib/libsemiprof.dll.a
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/semiprof.pc

